## Quickstart

```bash
cp .env.example .env
poetry install
poetry run uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

Open API docs at http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

## Run Tests

```bash
poetry run pytest
```

## Architecture

```text
app/
  core/     # config, DI, security
  api/v1/   # versioned API routes
  models/   # data models
  schemas/  # request/response DTOs
  crud/     # repository pattern
```

